window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The official prequel and origin story of the best-selling Extinction Cycle series! </b></p> <p>One marine’s end is the beginning of our extinction.... </p> <p>For a dozen years, villagers along the ancient Da River in Vietnam have feared a nightmarish creature who hunts and consumes human flesh. Only in whispers do they mention its name, The White Ghost.</p> <p>To the United States military, this creature has a different name - Marine Lieutenant Trevor Brett, the chemically engineered experiment gone wrong that they will do anything to hide. Sole survivor of his platoon, Brett has stalked the jungle for prey for over a decade. But the men who made him into a monster are searching for him, and when they find him, the line between hunter and hunted will be blurred.</p>"; 
